description: This channel highlights the work of Texas Christian University's Locomotor Performance Lab (LPL).  The LPL specializes in terrestrial locomotion and in relating muscle function to metabolic energy expenditure and performance. Current research focuses on the relationships between the mechanics of movement, performance, metabolic energy expenditure, and metabolic power. This research addresses scientific questions at the whole-body or organism level of biological organization, as well as addressing issues at the tissue and cellular levels.

description: 최신 IT 리뷰와 제품 리뷰를 주로 올립니다. IT 제품과 노트북, 컴퓨터, 스마트폰, 인테리어 등 다양한 제품에 관심이 많습니다. 직접 사용해고 가장 리얼한 리뷰 영상을 올립니다. 블로그도 운영을 하고 있어서 글로 된 리뷰를 올립니다. 글로 부족한 부분을 소개 하기 위해서 유튜브 채널을 운영 하고 있습니다. 저는 가장 진솔하고 정확한 리뷰를 올리기 위해서 많은 노력을 해오고 있습니다. 많은 테스터기를 구매해서 가지고 있는 이유도 좀 더 객관적이고 정확한 정보 전달을 위해서 입니다. 씨디맨 유튜브 채널은 그래서 신뢰도가 높은 채널로 알려져 있습니다. 더 좋은 정보를 전달하기 위해서 노력 하겠습니다.

With industry-leading turnaround times, News Direct's animations are available to customers hours after a top story breaks. News Direct launched on Reuters' global distribution system in July of 2012. Some 150 media outlets worldwide currently use News Direct's animations.  

For more information about News Direct or to sign up for the service, please visit http://newsdirect.nextanimation.com.tw/

description:
🚅 Japan Train Videos

Embark on a captivating journey with Kurt Bell, the author of "Going Alone" and a devoted family man, as he takes you along the vibrant railways of Japan 🚅. Explore the country's rich history and modern marvels through its extensive train network. From the bullet trains' swift elegance to the quaint charm of local lines, each journey reveals a unique aspect of Japan's heart and soul.

With Kurt's Stoic insights and recognition of life's inherent absence of meaning, the Japan Train Videos channel offers more than just scenic rides; it invites viewers to contemplate the deeper rhythms of life in motion.

Immerse yourself in the dynamic world of Japanese railways on the Japan Train Videos channel. Embrace the journey, discover the stories behind each route, and remember: Travel far, but always with purpose.

#JapanTrainVideos #KurtBell #RailwayAdventures 🚄🌆

description:
Anything goes here: retro gaming on pretty much every game system from 1977, cancerous clones, pathetic plug and plays and awesome indies from today. Hardware reviews of game systems, rare and common as well as every type of mobile gaming available. I truly play EVERYTHING. I try to cover only things I like, so if you are looking for some hate you are in the wrong place.

I can be contacted as Retr0Rob on XBox Live, Origin and Steam.

In real life I make a living in networking and security so I throw in some geeky tech stuff from time to time as well.

AI Use:
I try to mark the use of AI in videos when I can, but my general policy is:

I regularly use music performed by AI, but the lyrics are usually either created or heavily edited my me unless the ai comes up with something hilarious. 

My channel is NOT profitable. No-one is losing their job or any money to my use of AI. I use it to save time on production and fill in gaps in my skill -You totally do not want me sing.

description:
~Qur'an for everyone~

Feel free to download & share the audio: 

Part 1 (surah 1-10, 187mb): http://tinyurl.com/b5z72ez

Part 2 (surah 11-36, 178mb): http://tinyurl.com/agpfsjq

Part 3 (surah 37-98, 122mb): http://tinyurl.com/bd6p2vj

The fast Qur'an is meant for people who would like to recite the entire Qur'an but have difficulty, or for the month of Ramadhan, or as a tool to aid in memorising the Qur'an. This is meant for people who seriously need it. If you are listening with evil intentions then the sin is on you. If it's too fast for you, then clearly it's not meant for you, and you need to leave- don't bother leaving a comment. I have witnessed how this recitation helped people with genuine disabilities, and my conscience is clean. If you don't have those disabilities, then thank God, and move along.

Please recite a Suratul Fatihah for all mu'mineen.

~Salaams~

description:
Founded in 1992, by Zoran Momich, Z Automation Company, Inc. (ZAC) has grown at an astounding rate due to our commitment to quality and excellence. Our success is attributed to a family owned corporation's dedication to quality, value, and world class customer service. 
Our expansive and modern plant, located in Arlington Heights, Illinois houses a complete manufacturing process, assembling, business offices, and engineering departments. Over the years, ZAC has developed a complete end-of-line product portfolio which includes: Horizontal and Vertical Cartoning Systems, Sleeving Systems, Case and Tray Packers, Robotic Solutions, and Fully Integrated Systems. Our complete product line fulfills the needs of a wide variety of customers and a multitude of applications.

description: Hi everyone! Welcome to my little channel. The name is Karl and Psykult is one of my projects, the one that gets most time spent on it now. It blends metal with different electronic genres of music, somewhat a common trend these days, yet i tried to make it sound its own way. As of now it is in demo state, as it is entirely made in FL Studio and lacks vocals, so, if you're interested in helping me on that, feel free to pm me. I was influenced by such older bands like KMFDM, Front 242, Fear Factory and some modern electronic bands like Alien Vampires. Guess you can call them all industrial more or less, though i'm trying to take whatever i can from many genres of music. So, watch my videos, don't forget to switch to HD, rate and comment, and if you have any questions, pm me any time. Hope you enjoy my project.

description:
153 YEARS IN THE OUTDOORS
It all started in 1871, when an outerwear manufacturer—Gordon & Ferguson Merchandising Company—opened shop in St. Paul, Minnesota, and would go on to sell clothing under the "Field & Stream" brand. Almost 25 years later, in 1895, two hunting buddies got the idea for a magazine and soon published the first issue of Northwestern Field & Stream: A Journal of the Rifle, Gun, Rod and Camera. Two years later, the title was shortened simply to Field & Stream. The most recent chapter to the F&S story came in 2023, when, for the first time in the brand’s history, the media rights and licensing rights were all under one roof. While the magazine is still the heart and soul of the company, there are plenty of exciting things going on at F&S, including a line of fan merchandise, an upcoming country music festival, and a chain of hotels designed for hunters and anglers.

description:
The Kahr Firearms Group is a USA based firearms manufacturer which includes Kahr Arms, Thompson, Auto-Ordnance and Magnum Research. 

Kahr Arms produces a line of high-quality concealed carry pistols. Kahr's line includes firearms with polymer and stainless steel frames with stainless steel slides in four of the most popular calibers: .380 ACP, 9 mm, .40 S&W and .45 ACP.

Thompson/Auto-Ordnance Corporation is known as a maker of historical military firearms such as the M1 .30 Caliber Carbine, WWII 1911 .45 ACP Pistols, and semi-auto versions of the world famous "Tommy Gun."

Magnum Research Inc., is a manufacturer and importer  of the Desert Eagle pistols, Baby Eagle III pistols, BFR Revolvers, Desert Eagle 1911 pistols, Magnum Lite Rimfire, SwitchBolt and Centerfire Rifles.

Headquarters is located at 105 Kahr Ave., Greeley, PA 18425. Call us at (508) 795-3919.

description:
Welcome to JimLiElevators: My name is Jim and I am an elevator photographer based in central Texas. I have always loved elevators when I was a kid. Been filming since 2005. I present to you videos of elevators that are both vintage and modern. Not only that I film elevators, but I've also been interested into trains as well. I'll occasionally upload animated elevators because I've had a lot of fun making them. So with that said, I hope you enjoy your visit to my channel.

Thanks so much for your loyal viewership. I take pride in keeping this channel clean for all ages. I am also a born Christian, so I want to keep it pleasing to Jesus as well! “For God so loved the world that he gave his only son that believes in him shall not perish but have eternal life. John 3:16."

I'm also thankful to Andrew Reams (DieselDucy) who's the deepest inspiration towards me to start this channel. That said, make sure you subscribe. Thanks and have a great day! :D

description:
BlankTV is the Net's largest, DIY, free, uncensored music video site, featuring videos and live clips spanning the past forty years of punk, hardcore, metal, indie and underground music.

We grew up in the Boston hardcore scene in the 1980's - that's the music that inspired us, saved us and changed our lives.  That love of music drove the creation of our punk and hardcore website BlankTV in 1999, a way to trade live band videos with other punks online. 
We started getting traffic and we grew from there. We eventually made the jump to YouTube and decided to expand our featured genres to include other styles of music due to the overwhelming number of submissions that didn’t fit within punk rock.  
BlankTV is an inclusive community for all music lovers. 

We’ve been at this for twenty-five years and we hope to continue connecting our audience with their next favorite artist for many years to come.

Not bad for a couple of idiot teens from Boston with two laptops, a couch and a dream.

description:
This channel started out with a train video I made of my all time favorite train. the Southern Pacific GS-4 Daylight, SP4449, otherwise known as "The Freedom Train"
 I fell in love with this train when I first saw it in Portland Oregon, in its Red White & Blue Freedom Train colors.  It traveled across the US to celebrate our countries 200th Birthday, The US Bi-Centennial, in 1976.  I never suspected that video would get as many views as it did (and still is getting!), but since it did, I decided to upload as many videos as I could of the train, and I added in a few more various videos I have taken through the years.

description:
Smart Vision Lights' YouTube channel features postings for product videos, technical assistance, demonstrations, and applications. 

We revolutionized the machine vision lighting industry with a intelligent constant current driver in every machine light. All of our machine vision illuminators have the constant current driver integrated simplifying the installation process. Our LED arrays are specifically engineered for use in vision systems. The SMART driver has the option to run the machine light in a constant LED illumination including analog and variable intensity control. The analog feature allows 0-100% intensity control of the machine vision light through a 0-10VDC signal or manual potentiometer.  All lights can strobe utilizing NPN or PNP trigger signal. 

More information about Smart Vision Lights can be found on our website: https://smartvisionlights.com

description:
You can live in one of 2 ways: as if everything is a miracle, or as if nothing is a miracle.
I think everything is a miracle.
You can be anything you want, but you cannot be everything you want. You must decide what is important and focus.
These videos are about leadership: deciding what change is important, and bringing together the resources to achieve that change.

Questions? Ideas? Tweet me: http://www.twitter.com/conorneill  

About Conor...
Conor is a sought-after keynote speaker on leadership. As an entrepreneur, he has founded 4 companies, selling 16 private jets and building the 3rd largest fleet of private jets in Spain. He is a professor of Leadership at IESE Business School, and a visiting professor at University College Dublin. More about Conor: http://cono.rs/

description:
「ぼくたちにとって動いて見えるテレビ映像ですら、昆虫から見ればカタカタとした 動きにしか見えない。時間とはいったい何だろうか？」
時間を引きのばして昆虫の世界を見れば、そこには驚異の世界が見えてくる。私たちがスムーズに見えるテレビもカマキリが見たらコマ落としの映像にしかみえないだろう。（なにしろ獲物を捕る速度はわずか1/20秒である）
それほど昆虫の動きは早い。普通のビデオカメラではとらえきれない昆虫の動きや行動を高速度ビデオカメラを用いて時間を10倍から40倍に引き延ばして撮影している。
今では動画はビデオカメラだけでなくスチールカメラでも撮れる。このコーナーでは撮りだめた数々の動画や新しくスチールカメラで撮っている最新動画などを掲載していくことにする。

And now, for the first time, we are bringing to you the full story of what happened on that fateful day. We are bringing you all the evidence, based only on the secret testimony of the miserable souls who survived this terrifying ordeal. The incidents, the places. "SimonKr" was founded in 2005 by Simon Krzic and is currently one of the leading stock footage production companies in the industry. The main focus is to refine and perfect our proven approach to the production of high-quality stock footage. Early on, we submitted stills and footage to most of the major microstock websites, but in June 2007 exclusivity was signed with iStockvideo for the RF footage program and were soon invited to contribute to Getty Images as well.

The folks at iStock refer to us as "the most prolific videographer on the planet". With more than 20.000 active video files in our iStock portfolio, our work is likely to appear in almost any content search initiated at iStock. 

Our portfolio includes themes from everyday lifestyle, business concepts, wildlife, world-wide travel footage and mostly human emotions. You can check our portfolio here: http://www.simonkr.com/portfolio

description:
Welcome to the official Mazda Australia YouTube channel.

Zoom-Zoom is at the heart of everything we do. It’s a celebration of the joy of motion in all its forms. Whether that’s accelerating down an open road with the wind in your hair, off the beaten track, or being lulled to sleep in the backseat after a big day. description:
Walter Benjamin, singer/songwriter currently based in London - not to be confused with German philosopher, Walter Benjamin, who committed suicide on his way to Portugal - was born in Lisbon during the spring falling on the same day as Bob Dylan. Walter released his debut album, The National Crisis, (Merzbau) which was then followed by several EPs. 

He's toured throughout Europe, including being invited to play his three chord song, 'The Cannonball', at the Dadaist Centre in Zurich, Cabaret Voltaire, and has also produced and played with several artists.

Credits include; Jesus, the Misunderstood, Márcia, B Fachada, Julie & the Carjackers, Noiserv, Goodbye Toulouse, You Can't Win Charlie Brown, João Coração, Minta & the Brook Trout, to name a few.

description:
CaughtOnTapeTV is brought to you by the CONUS Archive and highlights amazing and interesting moments caught on tape over the years from police and surveillance videos, incredible rescues and disasters to the just plain bizarre and funny.  

In addition to the CaughtOnTapeTv channel, we've now added a channel entirely devoted to everything related to firefighters as we now how popular these type of clips are.  You can find the link to our latest channel on our home page.

Do you think you might have the next "viral" video?  Contact CaughtOnTapeTV before you post your video to the internet and learn how to make the most of your gem!

description:
Welcome to Ryan Michad's Handgun Radio Channel! Here I try to go over firearms that you may not see fired or reviewed elsewhere, along with high-speed footage of classic & modern firearms.  I really enjoy being able to showcase some of the interesting guns that I get to shoot, along with giving you a little bit of the history behind them. Many videos here are referenced in the Handgun Radio Podcast on the Firearms Radio Network! Be sure to go like the Handgun Radio Facebook Page as well!  I hope to upload a few videos a week, but with work and life, that can change depending upon events.  Please subscribe and share the videos and thank you very much for watching!!

Feel free to message me with any questions!

Also, check out our Facebook page at www.facebook.com/handgunradio for all your talk radio handgunning needs!

Visit www.firearmsradio.tv for Pro-Gun Radio!

Family owned, JOULIN invented the foam vacuum gripper over 60 years ago, we continue to pioneer advances in vacuum technology today.

Whether you are picking a complete layer, partial layer or single part, the JOULIN foam gripper automatically senses and closes the check valves in areas without product, allowing the same gripper to be used with no additional set up or re-programming.

From grippers to complete turnkey stacking and de-stacking systems, Joulin is flexible and offers a quick response to supply the best solution for you.
With manufacturing and design facilities in Europe and the USA, see for yourself why 60 countries and counting trust JOULIN for their lumber handling projects.

description:
“Inspiring images. Since 1917.” ARRI is a global player within the motion picture industry, employing around 1,200 staff worldwide. 
Named after its founders August Arnold and Robert Richter, ARRI was established in Munich, Germany, where the headquarters is still located today. Subsidiaries are in Europe, North and South America, Asia, and Australia. 
The ARRI Group consists of the business units Camera Systems, Lighting, and Rental, all dedicated to connecting creativity and future technologies for moving images. ARRI is a leading designer and manufacturer of camera and lighting systems as well as system solutions for the film, broadcast, and media industries, with a worldwide distribution and service network. The portfolio includes digital cameras, lenses, camera accessories, archive technologies, lamp heads, and lighting accessories. Along with offering exclusive technologies, ARRI Rental’s first-class services and equipment provide camera, lighting, and grip packages.

AIRBOYD • Creating and uploading aviation and aerospace videos since 2007 one of the most watched aviation channels on YouTube • AvGeek spoken here

As seen on ABC, ITV, AFP, NatGeo, Channel4, TruTV, Pearson Education, The Guardian, South China Morning Post and other productions like Most Extreme Airports, Richard Hammond's Engineering Connections, Crisis Averted, PilotsEye, LA to Vegas and more

About AIRBOYD: My original videos were taken in Hong Kong at Kai Tak airport prior to it being closed in 1998. My personal video is strictly amateur and any unrelated noise is just that. I started this to archive my footage but found there were other aviation fans. This led to compiling and scouring the internet for aviation films and videos of all sorts. There are videos and films about, training, safety, vintage aircraft and more. 

ALL OTHER VIDEOS credited from source where indicated in the description and elsewhere. 

High Quality versions available upon request for productions.

Mister C is a celebrity science teacher that makes learning fun!  He's a regional Emmy Award winner and 15-time Telly Award Winner for DIY Science Time. He travels all over the country with Mister C Live, which is a theatre science production. Visit  http://www.misterc.live to learn more or book Mister C.

Mister C is also an Ohio Valley Emmy Award winning producer for Speakers and Beakers and 3-time nominated host and producer for his series Full STEAM Ahead. 

When it comes to edutainment, Mister C has you covered! He was a 5th grade science teacher and elementary principal and knows how to connect with learners in a fun and creative way! 

WARNING: These videos are provided for entertainment and educational purposes only. It is your responsibility to evaluate the instructions and information contained in these videos. Have fun but remember to follow science safety, and everything you try is at YOUR OWN RISK!

description:
My location: Los Angeles, California USA

Uploading videos since 2005. Uploading personal videos on this channel since 2007.
Uploading my travels, adventures, hobbies, motorbikes, my political views, my help to my fellow mankind and more.

2015: I started to upload videos and films about giving help to people, mostly to Filipino folks. 
I've been reaching out and giving help to my fellow Filipinos since 2006, but without filming and uploading on YouTube.
I decided to film and upload the help we do/give to spread social awareness and for me to have means/ways of expressing my political, societal, social and economic sentiments/grievances.

This channel and I had been featured on some TV news segments in USA, Germany and the Philippines.  
You can watch the news segments on this channel. 

Due to the sensitivity of the videos I upload about poverty, abuse, exploitation and corruption: Google totally unplugged my YouTube Partner Program on June 9, 2025.
No ADS on this channel.

description:
IMATHIA Construcción, fundada en 2004, se establece a nivel nacional e internacional como empresa especializada en obra civil, con especial vocación por el sector ferroviario.
Con proyectos en los corredores principales de la península y alrededor del mundo, construyendo líneas de AV, convencionales, metros y trenes ligeros. Nuestra referencia más conocida es el AVE Meca Medina en Arabia Saudí (tendido de vía y mantenimiento). Actualmente trabajamos en la rehabilitación de la línea Kampala - Malaba (Uganda), en el nuevo taller de Fuencarral II (Madrid-España) y en la conexión ferroviaria del Puerto de Cádiz.

Be happy to leave me any comment or send me an inbox(suggestions, comments, complains, anything)

All of my videos were shot with my gopro Hd Hero 2, a perfect solution for people who wants to capture extreme sports or incredible demonstrations of anything.

Aimed Research is supported by professional talent that has designed programmable munitions, firing control systems and other electronics, though Aimed Research is not currently a manufacturer of any products. Aimed Research is open to work in-part or in-whole with your organization to provide accelerated results for your product development.

description:
We’re a weird hybrid studio/production company that, at our core, strives to bring you fun, genuine entertainment, whether it’s TV shows, feature films, short films, live streams, tutorials, or anything in-between. We pride ourselves on making better stories than you’d expect and with more heart than you’d imagine.

We started with Video Game High School, a three-season, full-length, award-winning independent web series. It was named #1 Web Series of 2013 by Variety, nominated for a Producer’s Guild Award for Outstanding Digital Series in 2014 and 2015, and won Streamy Awards for Direction, Ensemble Cast, and Action/Sci-Fi Series. Soon after, we partnered with Lionsgate, which resulted in the 2015 behind-the-scenes documentary series RocketJump: The Show on Hulu, our upcoming sci-fi anthology show Dimension 404, and a whole bunch more awesome stuff to come.

description:
View supplemental videos from our published reviews. 

Annual Reviews was founded in 1932 as a nonprofit organization dedicated to bringing the most comprehensive scientific review literature to its readers. Annual Reviews journals operate as a high quality filter, prioritizing and synthesizing the primary research literature in 46 different disciplines for the Biomedical, Life, Physical, and Social Sciences, including Economics. All topics for review are selected by an editorial committee comprised of the most distinguished scholars of the discipline. Annual Reviews articles are written by leading scholars to help researchers and students navigate the vast amount of primary research literature that is available to them. As a result, each article is its own search engine, providing a gateway to the most significant literature within a topic.

description:
Videos from the Robot Locomotion Group at the MIT Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence Laboratory. 

The goal of our research is to build machines which exploit their natural dynamics to achieve extraordinary agility and efficiency. We believe that this challenge involves a tight coupling between mechanical design and underactuated nonlinear control, and that tools from machine learning and optimal control can be used to produce this coupling when classical control techniques fail. Our projects include minimally-actuated dynamic walking on moderate terrain, quadrupedal locomotion on extreme terrain, fixed-wing acrobatics, flapping-winged flight, and feedback control for fluid dynamics.

The Robot Locomotion Group is a part of the CSAIL Center for Robotics.

description:
When I was a young boy (1950's), I learned to play golf by closely watching the best players at the course I grew up on. I would then stand in front of a window and copy their swings... then I would go to the practice area to ingrain that look and new feeling to muscle memory. That WAS and STILL IS a great way to learn! It's called SELF-DISCOVERY! 

When you discover a helpful motion or thought ALL BY YOURSELF, YOU WILL NEVER FORGET IT! - I never have!  

At the age of 78, I'm still a mid single-digit player. My goal with this YouTube channel is to provide a platform for TEACHING and LEARNING! I will provide videos and detailed descriptions of the finest golfers in the world, their swings and some of their finest shots so YOU can learn and improve as I have. 

The focus here is geared toward TEACHING and LEARNING the short game (putting, chipping, pitching and wedge play from 120-yards in), but you will also see some of the finest, Tour-Proven full swings and descriptions as well.⛳️

This channel introduces a number of full throttle driving scenes featuring Japanese vehicles.Mitsubishi, Subaru, Honda, Toyota, Mazda, Suzuki, Daihatsu...
